{"tid":1177583,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"望住Nike 返炒嘅Kobe 4 我諗起你","createTime":"2019-05-29T23:35:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-30T00:29:36.000Z","uid":96411,"like":6,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"785bb6d002b27dc83c6b3165ce1430816e7e426a","tid":1177583,"uid":96411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T23:35:16.000Z","msg":"又到咗呢一日<br />\n係我同Candy分手第6年嘅記念日<br />\n每一年嘅呢一日我都會去旺角朗豪坊門口懷念一下 <br />\n因為呢度就係我哋最後一次見面嘅地方 而同時間我都會有衝動WhatsApp揾返佢睇下佢過成點(當然其實都係想復合)<br />\n我一路行一路諗<br />\n我到底應唔應該搵佢<br />\n直到我見到佢<br />\n<br />\nKobe 4 Protro<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H42D7sz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH42D7sz.jpg&h=008cf359&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我人生中第一對籃球鞋<br />\n陪我征戰學界沙場 <br />\n踏遍港九新界街場<br />\n贏過無數比賽嘅籃球鞋<br />\n<br />\n我同佢分別嘅情景依然歷歷在目<br />\n我仲好記得著咗佢4年之後嘅某一日<br />\n我如常著佢落街場鬥波 <br />\n打打吓突然間拗柴<br />\n望一望對鞋<br />\n先發覺原來鞋底甩咗<br />\n就係咁 我對Kobe 4 就正式同我講拜拜<br />\n喺往後嘅日子我遇過好多唔同嘅鞋<br />\n有好貼地嘅D.Rose 3<br />\n包裹感極強嘅Curry 5<br />\n支撐度滿分嘅Harden vol. 2<br />\n但係冇一對俾到我Kobe 4 Protro 嘅感覺<br />\n<br />\n我望一望呢對咁新淨嘅Kobe 4 <br />\n唔知點解睇極都覺得唔係太靚<br />\n我哥時先發覺原來我鍾意嘅唔係對鞋<br />\n而係我同佢嘅回憶<br />\n回不去嘅回憶<br />\n「先生! 有興趣可以試吓喎!」<br />\n允記嘅職員笑笑口咁行埋黎同我講。<br />\n我冇答到佢<br />\n只係擰一擰頭 <br />\n同時放低咗對Kobe 4<br />\n<br />\n我諗有啲嘢都係留返喺個腦度比較好。"},{"pid":"fac7955a0afa5bd57cb677dcadd4fa109edccd77","tid":1177583,"uid":6070,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T23:36:17.000Z","msg":"facebook定xanga？"},{"pid":"97d0c032a79748574184527888fba09e80b6a54a","tid":1177583,"uid":174013,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T23:36:23.000Z","msg":"情聖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71abe860a679373748d6b1d371d4e5353d9c609e","tid":1177583,"uid":189109,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T23:38:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">冇人想知呀</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"578cbef9d84831bc104d060b97292e51090c4c75","tid":1177583,"uid":29784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T23:40:53.000Z","msg":"有無邊個想知？"},{"pid":"c28b6b8fd1697d1e35af94c9af743d64ed25afb8","tid":1177583,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T23:41:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">🤯</span>"},{"pid":"b1572dac3160ea5d995932b51b0b050019026091","tid":1177583,"uid":230439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T00:26:14.000Z","msg":"Kobe V"},{"pid":"20ad3e382052a098ed3a9304521ed9dfc3d395ab","tid":1177583,"uid":1880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T00:29:36.000Z","msg":"邊間允記有kobe4賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}